{"tid":438135,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前中文大學校長馬臨逝世，享年93歲","createTime":"2017-10-16T15:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T22:41:35.000Z","uid":35221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e603dd87bf55b87863dd714f9d01ca9d211e7152","tid":438135,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171016/s00001/79446beff16535ff02242a1eda5e8d05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171016%2Fs00001%2F79446beff16535ff02242a1eda5e8d05.jpg&h=fc389830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - （資料圖片 / 明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n香港中文大學前校長、逸夫書院創辦人馬臨教授離世，終年93歲。<br />\n<br />\n馬臨1947年在成都華西大學畢業後，曾赴英國深造，專研蛋白質化學研究並於1955年獲哲學博士銜。他1957年起出任中大講師，歷任高級講師、講座教授及理學院院長等，1978年起繼李卓敏出任第二任中大校長。直到1987年，他卸下校長身分創立逸夫書院，之後一直擔任校董會主席。<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171016/s00001/1508166558652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171016%2Fs00001%2F1508166558652&d=Uv8CczrRkfOF72xqJBGoN7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=0d2be56d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171016%2Fs00001%2F1508166558652&h=9d37ae46\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171016/s00001/1508166558652</a>"},{"pid":"84a18c5ca0182331b79fcf4aed76bc814f5db977","tid":438135,"uid":138809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171016/s00001/79446beff16535ff02242a1eda5e8d05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171016%2Fs00001%2F79446beff16535ff02242a1eda5e8d05.jpg&h=fc389830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - （資料圖片 / 明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n香港中文大學前校長、逸夫書院創辦人馬臨教授離世，終年93歲。<br />\n<br />\n馬臨1947年在成都